
```SuperCollider
(
SynthDef("diamond-graph", {
	| out, max = 100, n = 300 |
	x = SinOsc.ar(MouseX.kr(1, max));
	a = SinOsc.ar(n * x + 800, 0, 0.1);
	b = PinkNoise.ar(0.1 * x + 0.1);
	Out.ar(out, a + b);
}).writeDefFile("/tmp");
)
```
